title: Chola - Groove The Nation (Dirtball From Subnoize Records)
description:
This is Chola - Groove The Nation. The vocalist is better known today as The Dirtball from Suburban Noize Records.

He has 2 solo albums on the label, and has his 3rd full length called Crook County dropping May 13th 2008. Pre Order is available now at www.subnoizestore.com

The Dirtball is also involved with the Subnoize Souljaz, a compilation group of Suburban Noize Artists.

Peace and respects
